        <item>
            <title>《GTA 6》2025 年推出各平台但未有 PC　Fans 估計各版本售價圖</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/gta6-2025-on-ps5-xbox-x-s/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gta6-2025-on-ps5-xbox-x-s</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/gta6-2025-on-ps5-xbox-x-s/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:50:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[grand theft auto]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Grand Theft Auto VI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[gta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[rockstar]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Take-Two]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208711</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>距離《GTA 5》首發經已逾 10 年，遊戲開發商的母公司 Take-Two 日前終於發佈官方新聞稿確認《GTA 6》將於 2025 年內首先在 PS5、Xbox Series X|S 兩大家用機推出，不過暫時尚未公佈有關 PC 的細節。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_73061"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QdBZY2fkU-0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Rockstar 在香港時間今日早上 7 點於 YouTube 上發佈了《GTA 6》第一條預告片。預告片中可見 GTA 6 將採用以佛羅裏達邁亞密為原型的 Vice City 作遊戲地圖。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-40-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲預告片中可見大大的「VICE」字樣</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208716" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-33-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-31-screenshot-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-0-22-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>雙主角設計 + 首次有女性主角</h2><p>預告中同時亦可見有一男一女，相信是遊戲主角。如屬實的話這次是 GTA 系列首次有女性擔任主角。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-14-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>更多可進入建築物 + 打劫系統更完善</h2><p>知名遊戲資訊網站《Dexerto》早前曾報道指，網上流傳一份有關《GTA 6》的爆料文件。文件中表示《GTA 6》比以往全系列的 GTA 遊戲擁有更多可進入建築物，其中包括酒吧、當舖、脱衣舞俱樂部、超市、商店及部分住宅單位。據《Dexerto》報道指，以上種種可進入建築物均是為「打劫」系統而設。據悉《GTA 6》的打劫系統將會比上一代更強。Rockstar 官方上載的預告片亦有一男一女角色蒙面進入商店打劫的畫面。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/gta-6-buildings-leak-694x398.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="398" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/gta-6-buildings-leak-694x398.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/gta-6-buildings-leak.jpg 726w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-17-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Grand-Theft-Auto-VI-Trailer-1-1-9-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲官方上傳的預告顯示一對蒙面男女持槍進入商店的畫面</p><h2>傳地圖比《GTA 5》大 1.75 倍</h2><p>另外據爆料網站《High on Cinemaa》表示，與《GTA 5》Los Santos 的地圖相比，《GTA 6》Vice City 的地圖大了將近 1.75 倍。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GTA-6-Full-Map-Leak-and-Comparison-With-GTA-5-694x519.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="519" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GTA-6-Full-Map-Leak-and-Comparison-With-GTA-5-694x519.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/GTA-6-Full-Map-Leak-and-Comparison-With-GTA-5.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左邊為《GTA 6》地圖，右邊為《GTA 5》地圖<br />
圖片來源：<a href="https://highoncinemaa.com/high-on-gaming/gta-6-full-map-leak-and-comparison-with-gta-5/16670/">High on Cinemaa</a></p><p>Reddit 用户 @LivingSignificant555 就將兩張地圖重疊了起來（較深色部分位 GTA 6，較淺色部分為 GTA 5）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208728" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下載-1-584x580.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下載-1-584x580.jpg 584w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下載-1-907x900.jpg 907w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下載-1-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下載-1-768x762.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/下載-1.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 584px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左邊為《GTA 6》地圖，右邊為《GTA 5》地圖<br />
圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/GTA6/comments/16zbcqi/gta_v_map_size_vs_gta_vi_map_size/">LivingSignificant555@Reddit</a></p><h2>Fans 估計售價圖：最平 69.99、最貴 199.99 美元</h2><p>雖然現階段 Take-Two 尚未公佈售價，但有《GTA 6》的擁躉就已經為 Rockstar 製作好售價圖。<a href="https://twitter.com/GTAVI_Countdown">@GTAVI_Countdown</a> e 就在 X （前稱 Twitter）上發佈了自己製作的售價圖。@GTAVI_Countdown 預想 GTA6 會有 3 個價錢，最平的 《GTA 6》僅包含單機及 Online 版本，其預想售價為 69.99 美元；最貴的版本除了有單機、Online 版本外，亦包含了 2 位主角的 20 吋 figure、向前代 GTA Vice City 主角 Tommy Vercetti 致敬的 GTA 6 Online 遊戲服裝、OST、遊戲美術設定書冊、GTA 6 實體地圖及 10,000,000 GTA Online 遊戲貨幣。不知道官方會否參考 @GTAVI_Countdown 的模式售賣 《GTA 6》呢？真正價錢及版本尚要等待官方公佈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208736" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-694x466.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-694x466.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-1280x860.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-768x516.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-1536x1032.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/F5Nh_ypW8AAeTvy-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.take2games.com/ir/news/rockstar-games-announces-grand-theft-auto-vi-coming-2025">Take2Games</a>、<a href="https://highoncinemaa.com/high-on-gaming/gta-6-full-map-leak-and-comparison-with-gta-5/16670/">High on Cinemaa</a>、<a href="https://hothardware.com/news/gta6-map-size-hype">Hot Hardware</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/GTAVI_Countdown">GTAVI_Countdown@X</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gy