            <title>《GTA》三部曲重製版，手機版本發表 Netflix 訂户月中免費玩</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition-arrives-on-netflix/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition-arrives-on-netflix</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition-arrives-on-netflix/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 03:47:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影視娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy – The Definitive Edition]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Netflix]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208674</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>影視平台 Netflix 近年為用户提供超過 80 款免費遊戲，大部分都是與自家劇集或電影有關的遊戲小品，日前宣佈加入遊戲名單的《Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy &#8211; The Definitive Edition》則稍稍不同，既不是衍生自 Netflix 平台的影視作品，更加並非小品類遊戲。</p><p><span id="more-1208674"></span></p><p>這個《GTA》系列三部曲由《GTA III》、《GTA: Vice City》和《GTA: San Andreas》三款遊戲組成，它們原本都是 2001 至 2004 年期間推出的 AAA 級 PC 遊戲，兩年前經過重製並移植到 PlayStation、Xbox 和 Switch 等平台。現時遊戲終於登陸 Android 和 iOS 平台，官方聲稱遊戲畫面得以提升之餘，亦加入手機遊戲所需的觸控功能。玩家可以在 Liberty City、Vice City 和 San Andreas 三個城市中自由遊走和執行各樣任務。</p><p>遊戲商 Rockstar Games 未有公佈手機版《GTA: The Trilogy &#8211; The Definitive Edition》的上市安排，但就容許 Netflix 向客户免費提供，訂户可以由即日起登記，12 月 14 日開始就可以免費玩到。遊戲會透過 Netflix 流動程式提供，訂户亦可以透過 Apple App Store 或 Google Play Store 下載安裝。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_75093"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/D71cBUeAL58?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://about.netflix.com/en/news/grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition-arrives-on-netflix">netflix</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>====</p><h2>unwire learn 推出:</h2><p><strong>獨門 AI 用法助你工作及創業課程</strong><br /><a href="https://learn.unwire.hk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&lt;按此報名&gt;</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition-arrives-on-netflix/game-channel/">《GTA》三部曲重製版，手機版本發表 Netflix 訂户月中免費玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
